description: Try our easy to follow Feta & Veg-Loaded Muffins recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Feta & Veg-Loaded Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spoon mixture evenly into cases. Bake for 35 minutes or until a skewer inserted in the centre comes out clean. Stand in pan for 10 minutes, then transfer to a cooling rack. Top with remaining feta and extra mint. Serve.
